summary: An Ordinance transferring the sum of Two Hundred Thirty-three and 97/100 (233.97) Dollars, from Local Improvement District No. 1826 Fund, into the General Fund of the City of Seattle, for the purpose of reimbursing said General Fund, for the deficiency in the Fixed Estimate of said district, for the improvement of West Sixtieth Street, and other streets and avenues, by constructing sewers, under Ordinance No. 19018.
